  "description": "High-register granular shimmer using medium grains — 0.35 size — with bright filter and low posScatter. The shimmer comes from pitchScatter 0.08: grains detune slightly around the played note, creating the beating-partial characteristic of struck metal. High density, tight envelope. A cymbal that has forgotten it was ever a cymbal.",
